text:
Hwy 55 in Indian Land was delicious and everything was freshly made!  I had a Swiss and mushroom burger with fries and gravy!  The bun was warm and very soft!  I had a hot fudge sundae for dessert. It was very good!  My daughter and grandkids loved their food too!  We will be back again and again!  Thank you for the great food and service!  The manager personally checked if everyone was happy with their order.  Nice touch!
One suggestion:  Steak Fries :)  
Thank you!
